	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName> <date>May 22<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> 1835</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Well my Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee>&#44; I can hardly credit my<lb/> senses&#44; that I should have been nearly six months<lb/> in this city without receiving a <hi rend="underline">direct</hi> welcome <del>from<add>&#63;</add></del><lb/> among my dear family&#44; from one of my most valued<lb/> friends&#44; can it be picque or an imaginary slight<lb/> intendency on my part&#44; which has withheld the<lb/> desired satisfaction&#63;  I have been seemingly<lb/> neglectful&#44; yet a prince should consider how<lb/> many circumstances <hi rend="underline">may</hi> prevent a mother of<lb/> almost four <hi rend="underline">infants</hi> and her own health<lb/> never very good&#44; from being a punctual correspon<lb/>&#61;dant&#8212;I intended to have immediately written<lb/> you when I heard of your loss&#44; but really at that<lb/> time some circumstance important to my family<lb/> prevented&#44; and I felt my total inability to offer<lb/> consolation&#44; when I needed it so much myself<lb/> forgive my friend&#44; all apparent neglect I <hi rend="underline">am</hi> <hi rend="underline">as</hi><lb/> attached to you as in former times if I know<lb/> my own heart&#44; and should be highly pleased to</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>have you a resident among us so that my child<lb/>&#61;ren could be as much <sic>benefitted</sic> by that<lb/> society&#40;<add>the <sic>deprevation</sic><add>&#63;</add> of</add> which has been truly regretted by their<lb/> mother&#41; as she has been&#44; I will not <sic>dispair</sic> but<lb/> trust my beloved Creator&#44; who has so far listened<lb/> to my prayers&#44; restoring me to my dear family w<add>&#63;</add><lb/> Will reunite me with my friends&#8212;I cannot<lb/> write you a long letter at present as I am<lb/> very busy making my children clothes for the<lb/> warm weather&#44; when through I will write<lb/> more fully <sic>untill</sic> when believe me<lb/> as ever unalterably your friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">A Block</persName></p>
				<p>My love to <persName>Mrs Lyon</persName>&#44; <persName>Allen</persName> &#38;c</p>
			<pb n="2V"/>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">attention of Uncle</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><persName>Rehine</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">W G P &#8212;</p>
		</body>
